Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:13.67,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.61,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 柊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.47,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
